><p class="max-w-screen-lg font-serif lg:text-xl"></p><div class="mt-12 mb-4 first:mt-0 lg:first:mt-12"><h2 class="font-bold font-sans-heading text-2xl leading-7 lg:text-3xl xl:text-4xl">Events</h2></div><section class="mb-4"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 sm:gap-6 md:grid-cols-2"><div class="flex justify-between gap-3 border-t border-gray-200 pt-4"><a href="/uk/events/teenage-kicks-girls-growing-up-in-britain-in-the-sixties-13112" class="group flex w-full items-start gap-2 gap-6"><section class="flex basis-3/4 flex-col items-start gap-2"><span class="group-hover:text-indigo-600 group-hover:underline"><h5 class="font-bold font-sans-heading text-base leading-5 lg:text-lg lg:leading-6"><span>Teenage Kicks: Girls growing up in Britain in the sixties</span></h5></span><p class="text-3xs text-gray-600 line-clamp-4">University of Manchester</p></section><div class="relative aspect-square basis-1/4"><img alt="Teenage Kicks: Girls growing up in Britain in the sixties" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="object-contain" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent;background-size:cover;background-position:50% 50%;background-repeat:no-repeat;background-image:url(&quot;data:image/svg+xml;charset=utf-8,%3Csvg xmlns=&#x27;http%3A//www.w3.org/2000/svg&#x27;%3E%3Cimage style=&#x27;filter:blur(20px)&#x27; preserveAspectRatio=&#x27;none&#x27; x=&#x27;0&#x27; y=&#x27;0&#x27; height=&#x27;100%25&#x27; width=&#x27;100%25&#x27; href=&#x27;data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAPAAAAAAAP///yH5BAAAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==&#x27;/%3E%3C/svg%3E&quot;)" sizes="(min-width: 1466px) 169.5px, (min-width: 1024px) 121.5px, (min-width: 640px) 12.5vw, 25vw" srcSet="https://images.theconversation.com/institutions/1204/logos/logo-1371440970.png?ixlib=rb-4.1.0&amp;q=45&amp;auto=format?q=30&amp;usm=12&amp;cs=strip&amp;w=256&amp;auto=format 256w, https://images.theconversation.com/institutions/1204/logos/logo-1371440970.png?ixlib=r